AERONAVES SERVES
ALL MAJOR TOURIST
AREAS WITHIN MEXICO
GENERAL INFORMATION
RESERVATION RECONFIRMATION
Return reservations for international flights must be recon-
firmed 72 hours before departure or they will be cancelled
... and 24 hours before departure on domestic services within
Mexico.
TOURIST CARD
Aeronaves' offices and the Mexican Govt. Tourjst Office will
issue cards upon receipt of proof of citizenship (birth certifi-
cate or voter's registration).
FREE BAGGAGE ALLOWANCE
44 Ibs. per tourist ticket and 66 Ibs. per first class ticket.
55 Ibs. for flights within Mexico.
ARRIVAL AT AIRPORT OF EMBARKATION:
Passengers should arrive at the airport at least one full hour
before scheduled departure time in order to complete neces-
sary Government and airline formalities.
VACCINATION
International Certificate of Inoculation and Vaccination for
smallpox (obtained within last 3 yrs.) required for travel to
and from Mexico to U.S. Call your local U.S. Health Service
for information.
